<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>상담 답변 완료</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Malgun Gothic', Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
        }
        .container {
            background: white;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            border-bottom: 3px solid #28a745;
            padding-bottom: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .logo {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #28a745;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .title {
            font-size: 20px;
            color: #2c3e50;
            margin: 0;
        }
        .reply-badge {
            background-color: #d4edda;
            color: #155724;
            border: 1px solid #c3e6cb;
            border-radius: 50px;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            display: inline-block;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .content {
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .greeting {
            font-size: 16px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .info-box {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            border-left: 4px solid #28a745;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .consultation-summary {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            border: 1px solid #dee2e6;
            border-radius: 5px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .consultation-summary h3 {
            color: #495057;
            margin-top: 0;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        .original-message {
            background-color: #e9ecef;
            border-left: 4px solid #6c757d;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 15px 0;
            border-radius: 0 5px 5px 0;
        }
        .reply-message {
            background-color: #d1ecf1;
            border-left: 4px solid #17a2b8;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 15px 0;
            border-radius: 0 5px 5px 0;
        }
        .expert-info {
            background-color: #e8f5e8;
            border: 1px solid #28a745;
            border-radius: 5px;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
        }
        .expert-avatar {
            width: 50px;
            height: 50px;
            background-color: #28a745;
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            color: white;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-right: 15px;
        }
        .expert-details h4 {
            margin: 0 0 5px 0;
            color: #155724;
        }
        .expert-details p {
            margin: 0;
            color: #6c757d;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        .additional-notes {
            background-color: #fff3cd;
            border: 1px solid #ffeaa7;
            border-radius: 5px;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-left: 4px solid #ffc107;
        }
        .next-actions {
            background-color: #d1ecf1;
            border: 1px solid #bee5eb;
            border-radius: 5px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-left: 4px solid #17a2b8;
        }
        .next-actions h3 {
            color: #0c5460;
            margin-top: 0;
        }
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #28a745;
            color: white !important;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin: 10px 5px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .button.secondary {
            background-color: #17a2b8;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 30px;
            padding-top: 20px;
            border-top: 1px solid #eee;
            color: #7f8c8d;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        .contact-info {
            background-color: #ecf0f1;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .rating-section {
            text-align: center;
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <div class="logo">VietnamVisa24</div>
            <h1 class="title">✅ 상담 답변 완료</h1>
        </div>

        <div class="content">
            <div style="text-align: center;">
                <div class="reply-badge">📞 전문가 답변 완료</div>
            </div>

            <div class="greeting">
                안녕하세요, <strong>{{customerName}}</strong>님
            </div>

            <div class="info-box">
                <strong>상담 번호:</strong> {{consultationId}}<br>
                <strong>서비스 유형:</strong> {{serviceType}}<br>
                <strong>답변 일시:</strong> {{repliedAt}}
            </div>

            <p>귀하의 베트남 비자 상담에 대한 전문가 답변을 보내드립니다.</p>

            <div class="consultation-summary">
                <h3>📋 원본 문의 내용</h3>
                <div class="original-message">
                    <h4>고객 문의:</h4>
                    <p style="white-space: pre-wrap;">{{originalMessage}}</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="expert-info">
                <div class="expert-avatar">
                    {{#if repliedBy}}{{repliedBy.[0]}}{{else}}전{{/if}}
                </div>
                <div class="expert-details">
                    <h4>{{repliedBy}}</h4>
                    <p>베트남 비자 전문 상담사</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="consultation-summary">
                <h3>💡 전문가 답변</h3>
                <div class="reply-message">
                    <h4>상담사 답변:</h4>
                    <p style="white-space: pre-wrap;">{{replyMessage}}</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            {{#if additionalNotes}}
            <div class="additional-notes">
                <h4>📝 추가 안내사항</h4>
                <p style="white-space: pre-wrap;">{{additionalNotes}}</p>
            </div>
            {{/if}}

            <div class="next-actions">
                <h3>🚀 다음 단계 안내</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>비자 신청:</strong> 답변을 참고하여 비자 신청을 진행하세요</li>
                    <li><strong>추가 문의:</strong> 더 궁금한 점이 있으시면 언제든 연락주세요</li>
                    <li><strong>서류 준비:</strong> 필요한 서류를 미리 준비해 두시면 빠른 처리가 가능합니다</li>
                    <li><strong>예약 상담:</strong> 전화 상담이 필요하시면 예약해 주세요</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div style="text-align: center;">
                <a href="/apply" class="button">지금 비자 신청하기</a>
                <a href="{{portalUrl}}" class="button secondary">상담 내역 확인</a>
            </div>

            <div class="rating-section">
                <h4>⭐ 상담 만족도 평가</h4>
                <p>저희 상담 서비스는 어떠셨나요?</p>
                <div style="margin: 15px 0;">
                    <a href="/feedback/{{consultationId}}?rating=5" style="text-decoration: none; margin: 0 5px; font-size: 24px;">⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐</a>
                    <a href="/feedback/{{consultationId}}?rating=4" style="text-decoration: none; margin: 0 5px; font-size: 24px;">⭐⭐⭐⭐</a>
                    <a href="/feedback/{{consultationId}}?rating=3" style="text-decoration: none; margin: 0 5px; font-size: 24px;">⭐⭐⭐</a>
                </div>
                <p style="font-size: 12px; color: #6c757d;">별점을 클릭하여 평가해 주세요</p>
            </div>

            <div class="contact-info">
                <h3>📞 추가 문의</h3>
                <p>더 자세한 상담이 필요하시면 언제든 연락해 주세요:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>전화:</strong> 1588-0000 (평일 09:00~18:00)</li>
                    <li><strong>카카오톡:</strong> @vietnamvisa24</li>
                    <li><strong>WhatsApp:</strong> +84-93-721-7284</li>
                    <li><strong>이메일:</strong> support@vietnamvisa24.com</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <p style="text-align: center; margin-top: 30px;">
                <strong>즐거운 베트남 여행을 위해 최선을 다하겠습니다! 🌟🇻🇳</strong>
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <p><strong>VietnamVisa24</strong></p>
            <p>📞 1588-0000 | 📧 support@vietnamvisa24.com</p>
            <p>평일 09:00~18:00 (토/일/공휴일 휴무)</p>
            <p style="font-size: 12px; color: #95a5a6; margin-top: 15px;">
                본 메일은 발신전용입니다. 문의사항이 있으시면 고객센터로 연락해 주세요.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
